name: Orb Weaver II
description:
Motherstar.

Process: A Sony KV-13FM12, Sony HVC-2400, Sony XV-5000, Panasonic AG-MX70, Panasonic WJ-MX50A, Panasonic WJ-MX30, Focus Enhancements MX-4DV, ADC V-300X, Akai PS-V20U, Sony XV-C900, Futek FA403, Yagi AV-EC3, ADC V-300, and Videonics VE-1A dreaming of each other, through each other. Final output stabilized and enhanced via For.A FA-370.

Direct capture via Canopus ADVC-110, edited in Adobe Premiere Pro, played back through a Sony KV-13FM12, and rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning an Asahi Super-Multi-Coated Macro-Takumar 1:4/50, interfaced direct to computer via HDMI to Blackmagic Design UltraStudio Recorder 3G and OBS Studio. 

Footage edited in Adobe Premiere Pro, then composed, colour graded and rendered in Adobe After Effects and converted with HandBrake.
